{"tid":477140,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺人愈大，好似愈來愈少開心","createTime":"2017-11-22T17:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T00:56:38.000Z","uid":22323,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"da947906a28590c1e66e3d105750b4040b07b375","tid":477140,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:05:39.000Z","msg":"宜家成個社會都充滿住負能量<br />\n每次睇新聞，見到既都只會令自己唔開心<br />\n個政府愈來愈赤化，當權者既得利益者個個逆民所思<br />\n睇返香港，見唔到將來<br />\n但自己無野可以做到<br />\n每日返工為左d乜<br />\n好彩仲有女朋友，如果唔係我諗唔到周圍仲有咩令我開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n童年愉快因太易叫好 <br />\n期求的多麼簡單 自能做到<br />\n數指甲也當嗜好 <br />\n得一個蠟燭加蛋糕 已想起舞<br />\n人大了沒有快樂除手到"},{"pid":"1325adc5ba4b6a9b42fa1ee4923288cc2e2f5011","tid":477140,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a2b5a319466e7b9c4ded0a89a14357bb15cf60","tid":477140,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f2a122585a08ebd03407ae2407d0926d2528e64","tid":477140,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"好彩我童年唔算好開心"},{"pid":"18ba0c767a062c169070a3b57c9ae4792e102bbd","tid":477140,"uid":4626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩我童年唔算好開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知應該開心定唔開心 so sad"},{"pid":"5f1765035592f000ec09bec39fd26f6f5576194c","tid":477140,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩我童年唔算好開心</blockquote><br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c99b72020e33